	<h2 id="pratilipi">Pratilipi</h2>
	<p>
		We believe in the age old adage: <i>"You become what you read"</i>, and that's why we want us to be able to.
	</p>
	<ol>
		<li>
			<span>
				<b><i>Read</i></b> whatever we want, whenever we want and wherever we want. Read from any device: computer, tablet or smartphone. Read in any language: Hindi, English, Tamil or Gujarati. Read carelessly. That's what paradise is: no file downloads, no format issues, no compatibility problems and oh loads and loads of books and poems and stories.
			</span>
		</li>
		<li>
			<span>
				<b><i>Discover</i></b> India's most celebrated authors, and the hidden gems. Read poems, Stories, Haiku, Books and much more. Follow your favorite authors, meet your new favorites, discover the joy of stumbling upon the best literature ever written.
			</span>
		</li>
		<li>
			<span>
				<b><i>Build</i></b> Create bookshelves, manage and arrange your books as you wish. Keep it private or share it with others. You can even build your wishlist and we might just gift you some of those books you wish to read ;)
			</span>
		</li>
		<li>
			<span>
				<b><i>Share</i></b> Read something that you liked ? Have something to say about a book that you read ? Have written a poem that you want us to read ? A book that you want to publish ? Share it with the pratilipi community, we want to read, did we tell you that we LOVE reading ?
			</span>
		</li>
		<li>
			<span>
				<b><i>Celebrate</i></b> We love celebrations (who doesn't, right ?). We celebrate the best poems, best stories, best books, best reviews and the best members.
			</span> 
		</li>
	</ol>
	<p>
		Join us today to read, share and celebrate with us.
	</p>
	
	
